<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><strong>Note: These are different from the <a href="/main">main</a> page's news and the <a href="/archived-news">Archived News</a>. Those are for live updates on the site's workings, policies, and projects. This is a summary for site articles and fandom creations for the month in whole, posted at the beginning of each month. If you wish to comment on this news series as a whole, or make suggestions, please comment on this hub instead of the individual pages. Please do not add rating modules to any of the individual pages.</strong></p>
