<li><a href="/scp-5583">SCP-5583</a> (&quot;Skippy the Unicorn Has Had Enough of Your Shit&quot;) - So, Skippy the Unicorn would like to tell you to go fuck yourself if you haven't already. Skippy is not Nickthebrick1's imaginary friend.</li>
